## 8. JSON Formatting Rules

- Use Python `json.dump(indent=4, sort_keys=True)` for consistent formatting
- Never use PowerShell `ConvertTo-Json` (adds wrong indentation)
- All `.info` files must be ASCII encoded, no BOM, Unix line endings (`\n`)

## 9. TDS PDF Handling

- Always download the manufacturer's TDS PDF when available
- Save in the filament's brand folder: `<Brand>\<Brand>_<Material>_TDS.pdf`
- Extract and verify all printing parameters against profile values
- Include TDS download link in README.md
- Key TDS data to extract: nozzle temp, bed temp, retraction distance/speed, density, Tg, HDT, Vicat, melting temp, drying temp, max print speed

